      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "text": "Auth:         Supabase SSR (@supabase/ssr) — server-side session via cookies. Middleware checks session on every request.\n              No localStorage. Fix: drop recursive RLS policy on organization_members → use security definer function.\n\nData fetching: Server Components fetch data at request time (no client fetch waterfalls).\n              useChat hook (AI SDK) handles streaming chat in client component island.\n              Server Actions for mutations (create thread, rename, pin, delete, upload).\n\nStyling:      Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui. CSS variables for brand colours (branding page writes to :root).\n\nAI streaming: useChat from @ai-sdk/react. Backend route.ts POST handler pipes Soapbox API SSE → Vercel streaming response.\n              Artifacts rendered in <iframe sandbox> to prevent XSS. ActivityStream shows tool calls inline.\n\nFile uploads:  Direct upload to Soapbox API via multipart form. Indexing status polled via EventSource.\n\nDeployment:    Vercel. Env vars: NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY, SOAPBOX_API_URL, SOAPBOX_API_KEY.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "seed": 4003,
      "version": 1
    }
